FRMCS - Handover RBC : Diagrammes de sequence avec payloads
Legende des niveaux de payload
•	[ETCS] : messages et paquets SUBSET-026 avec champs et longueurs en bits
•	[CFM] : primitives SUBSET-037-3 T-CONNECT / T-DISCONNECT / T-DATA
•	[NRBC] : messages inter-RBC SUBSET-039 avec header 9 champs
•	[TCP] : connexion TCP over FRMCS bearer
•	[5G] : signalisation 5G NR Registration, PDU Session
Acteur	Role
ETCS OBU	Unite bord ETCS - produit/consomme les messages SUBSET-026
OB FRMCS GW TOBA	Passerelle bord OB-GTW - gere CFM, routage IP, bearer flexibility TOBA-7510
OB FRMCS RF	Module radio 5G NR bord - UE 5G - 1 ou 2 instances selon scenario
FRMCS TS GW	Passerelle cote voie TSapp GW - point entree FRMCS vers RBC FIS-7970
RBC1	Radio Block Centre cedant Handing Over RBC
RBC2	Radio Block Centre acceptant Accepting RBC
References : SUBSET-026 v4.0.0, SUBSET-037-3 v4.1.4, SUBSET-039 v3.2.0, TOBA-7510 v1.0.0, TOBA-7540, FFFIS-7950, FIS-7970
________________________________________
Scenario 1 - Handover RBC sans changement de reseau FRMCS intra-PLMN
Session 5G maintenue sur PLMN-A tout au long du handover. Seule la destination TCP de la session EuroRadio change RBC1 vers RBC2. Architecture : un seul module RF actif.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant OBU as ETCS OBU
    participant GW as OB FRMCS GW TOBA
    participant RF as OB FRMCS RF
    participant TSGW as FRMCS TS GW
    participant RBC1 as RBC1 Handing Over
    participant RBC2 as RBC2 Accepting

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 0 - Situation nominale
    Note over OBU,GW: [ETCS] Header SUBSET-026 par7<br/>NID_MESSAGE 8b | L_MESSAGE 10b | T_TRAIN 32b | M_ACK 1b | NID_LRBG 24b
    OBU->>GW: [ETCS] T-DATA.request SafeData<br/>SUBSET-026 msg encapsule safety layer SUBSET-037-2
    GW->>RF: [TCP] flow dst=IP_RBC1:19990 TcpUserTimeout=300s
    RF-->>TSGW: [5G] NR DRB QoS ETCS PLMN-A
    TSGW-->>RBC1: [TCP] EuroRadio session active

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 1 - Preparation inter-RBC SUBSET-039
    Note over RBC1,RBC2: [NRBC] Header 9 champs<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE 8b | L_MESSAGE 10b | T_NRBC 32b<br/>NID_SENDER 14b | NID_RECEIVER 14b<br/>NID_C_SENDER 10b | NID_C_RECEIVER 10b<br/>NID_OPERATIONAL 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b
    RBC1->>RBC2: [NRBC] Handover Announcement<br/>Body: Q_SCALE 2b | D_RBCTR 15b | MA context packets 21 et 27
    RBC2-->>RBC1: [NRBC] Handover Announcement ACK<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE ACK | T_NRBC 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 2 - Ordre de handover vers OBU SUBSET-026
    Note over RBC1,TSGW: [ETCS] RBC1 compose Msg 24 General Message avec Packet 131 RBC Transition Order
    RBC1->>TSGW: [ETCS] Msg 24 + Packet 131<br/>NID_PACKET=131 8b | Q_DIR 2b | L_PACKET=69 13b<br/>Q_SCALE 2b | D_RBCTR 15b<br/>NID_C=NID_C_RBC2 10b | NID_RBC=ID_RBC2 14b<br/>NID_MN=PLMN_A 6x4b=24b | Q_RBC 1b<br/>PHONE_NUMBER=RBC2_SIP 8x4b=32b
    TSGW->>GW: [CFM] T-DATA.indication SafeData forward SUBSET-026 vers OBU
    GW->>OBU: [ETCS] Packet 131 delivre<br/>OBU extrait NID_C_RBC2 | NID_RBC2 | PHONE_NUMBER_RBC2

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 3 - Etablissement session EuroRadio vers RBC2
    OBU->>GW: [CFM] T-CONNECT.request FRMCS_CED_RBC2<br/>CED={NID_RBC2, IP_RBC2, port=19990, PLMN_A, QoS_ETCS}
    Note over GW,RF: Bearer 5G PLMN-A reutilise - pas de nouvelle PDU Session
    GW->>RF: [TCP] SYN dst=IP_RBC2:19990 MSS=1400 TcpUserTimeout=300s
    RF-->>TSGW: [5G] NR DRB existant route vers IP_RBC2
    TSGW-->>RBC2: [TCP] SYN nouvelle session EuroRadio entrante
    RBC2-->>TSGW: [TCP] SYN-ACK
    TSGW-->>GW: [TCP] ESTABLISHED
    GW-->>OBU: [CFM] T-CONNECT.confirm CID_RBC2 status=OK
    Note over OBU,RBC2: [ETCS] Session initiale make-before-break SUBSET-026 par3.5.3<br/>OBU->RBC2: Msg 155 NID_MESSAGE=155 | T_TRAIN 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b<br/>RBC2->OBU: Msg 32 NID_MESSAGE=32 | T_TRAIN 32b | M_VERSION 7b<br/>RBC2->OBU: Msg 38 NID_MESSAGE=38 | T_TRAIN 32b | NID_LRBG 24b

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 4 - Notification RBC2 vers RBC1 SUBSET-039
    RBC2->>RBC1: [NRBC] Train Accepted<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE Train_Accepted | T_NRBC 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 5 - Liberation session RBC1
    Note over OBU,GW: [ETCS] Liberation SUBSET-026 par3.5.4<br/>OBU->RBC1: Msg 156 NID_MESSAGE=156 | T_TRAIN 32b<br/>RBC1->OBU: Msg 39 NID_MESSAGE=39 | T_TRAIN 32b
    OBU->>GW: [CFM] T-DISCONNECT.request CID_RBC1 cause=NORMAL_RELEASE
    GW->>RF: [TCP] FIN dst=IP_RBC1:19990
    RF-->>TSGW: [5G] TCP close over PLMN-A DRB
    TSGW-->>RBC1: [TCP] FIN-ACK session released
    RBC1-->>RBC2: [NRBC] Handover Complete<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE HO_Complete | T_NRBC 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 6 - Operation nominale sous RBC2
    OBU->>GW: [ETCS] T-DATA.request SafeData SUBSET-026 vers RBC2
    GW->>RF: [TCP] flow dst=IP_RBC2:19990 PLMN-A inchange
    RF-->>TSGW: [5G] NR DRB PLMN-A session active
    TSGW-->>RBC2: [ETCS] EuroRadio session operationnelle
