Scenario 2 - Handover RBC avec changement de reseau FRMCS inter-PLMN franchissement de frontiere
RBC2 est raccorde a PLMN-B. L OB FRMCS GW TOBA active un second module RF bearer flexibility TOBA-7540 pre-enregistre sur PLMN-B. Les deux sessions coexistent make-before-break inter-PLMN avant liberation du bearer PLMN-A.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant OBU as ETCS OBU
    participant GW as OB FRMCS GW TOBA
    participant RF1 as OB FRMCS RF1 PLMN-A
    participant RF2 as OB FRMCS RF2 PLMN-B
    participant TSGW_A as FRMCS TS GW PLMN-A
    participant TSGW_B as FRMCS TS GW PLMN-B
    participant RBC1 as RBC1 Handing Over PLMN-A
    participant RBC2 as RBC2 Accepting PLMN-B

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 0 - Situation nominale sur PLMN-A
    OBU->>GW: [ETCS] T-DATA.request SafeData EuroRadio RBC1<br/>NID_MESSAGE 8b | L_MESSAGE 10b | T_TRAIN 32b | M_ACK 1b | NID_LRBG 24b
    GW->>RF1: [TCP] dst=IP_RBC1:19990 TcpUserTimeout=300s
    RF1-->>TSGW_A: [5G] NR DRB PLMN-A QoS ETCS
    TSGW_A-->>RBC1: [TCP] EuroRadio session active PLMN-A
    Note over GW,RF2: [5G] RF2 pre-enregistre PLMN-B bearer flexibility TOBA-7540<br/>Registration effectue - PDU Session idle ou pre-established

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 1 - Preparation inter-RBC SUBSET-039
    Note over RBC1,RBC2: [NRBC] Interface via reseau fixe inter-operateur IP backbone
    RBC1->>RBC2: [NRBC] Handover Announcement<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE 8b | L_MSG 10b | T_NRBC 32b<br/>NID_SENDER 14b=RBC1 | NID_RECEIVER 14b=RBC2<br/>NID_C_SENDER 10b | NID_C_RECEIVER 10b<br/>NID_OPERATIONAL 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b<br/>Body: Q_SCALE 2b | D_RBCTR 15b | MA context | Q_RBC 1b
    RBC2-->>RBC1: [NRBC] Handover Announcement ACK<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE ACK | T_NRBC 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 2 - Ordre de handover OBU SUBSET-026 Packet 131
    RBC1->>TSGW_A: [ETCS] Msg 24 + Packet 131 RBC Transition Order<br/>NID_PACKET=131 8b | Q_DIR 2b | L_PACKET=69 13b | Q_SCALE 2b<br/>D_RBCTR 15b<br/>NID_C=NID_C_RBC2 10b country PLMN-B<br/>NID_RBC=ID_RBC2 14b<br/>NID_MN=PLMN_B 6x4b=24b reseau PLMN-B<br/>Q_RBC 1b<br/>PHONE_NUMBER=SIP_URI_RBC2 8x4b=32b contact PLMN-B
    TSGW_A->>GW: [CFM] T-DATA.indication SafeData forward P131 vers OBU
    GW->>OBU: [ETCS] Packet 131 delivre<br/>OBU detecte NID_MN=PLMN_B different de PLMN_A<br/>OBU demande connexion PLMN-B a GW

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 3 - Activation bearer PLMN-B Bearer Flexibility TOBA-7540
    OBU->>GW: [CFM] T-CONNECT.request FRMCS_CED_RBC2<br/>CED={NID_RBC2, IP_RBC2, port=19990, PLMN_B, QoS_ETCS}
    Note over GW,RF2: [5G] GW selectionne RF2 deja enregistre PLMN-B<br/>Si PDU Session idle : Service Request 5G NAS vers AMF_B
    GW->>RF2: [5G] PDU Session activation PLMN-B<br/>NAS Service Request vers AMF_B<br/>PDU_Session_ID | S-NSSAI ETCS | DNN railway
    RF2-->>TSGW_B: [5G] NR RRC Reconfiguration + DRB etabli PLMN-B<br/>GTP-U tunnel etabli
    TSGW_B-->>GW: [5G] PDU Session active IP_RF2_PLMNB assignee

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 4 - Etablissement session EuroRadio vers RBC2 sur PLMN-B
    GW->>RF2: [TCP] SYN dst=IP_RBC2:19990 bearer PLMN-B<br/>src=IP_RF2_PLMNB TcpUserTimeout=300s
    RF2-->>TSGW_B: [5G] NR DRB PLMN-B TCP SYN route
    TSGW_B-->>RBC2: [TCP] SYN recu interface ETCS
    RBC2-->>TSGW_B: [TCP] SYN-ACK
    TSGW_B-->>GW: [TCP] ESTABLISHED IP_RF2_PLMNB to IP_RBC2
    GW-->>OBU: [CFM] T-CONNECT.confirm CID_RBC2 status=OK PLMN=B
    Note over OBU,RBC2: [ETCS] Session initiale OBU->RBC2 SUBSET-026 par3.5.3<br/>OBU->RBC2: Msg 155 NID_MESSAGE=155 | T_TRAIN 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b<br/>RBC2->OBU: Msg 32 NID_MESSAGE=32 | T_TRAIN 32b | M_VERSION 7b=4<br/>RBC2->OBU: Msg 38 NID_MESSAGE=38 | T_TRAIN 32b | NID_LRBG 24b
    Note over GW: [CFM] Deux sessions EuroRadio coexistent SUBSET-026 par5.15<br/>CID_RBC1 PLMN-A active + CID_RBC2 PLMN-B active

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 5 - Notification RBC2 vers RBC1 SUBSET-039
    RBC2->>RBC1: [NRBC] Train Accepted<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE Train_Accepted | T_NRBC 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 6 - Liberation session RBC1 et bearer PLMN-A
    Note over OBU,GW: [ETCS] Liberation SUBSET-026 par3.5.4<br/>OBU->RBC1: Msg 156 NID_MESSAGE=156 | T_TRAIN 32b<br/>RBC1->OBU: Msg 39 NID_MESSAGE=39 | T_TRAIN 32b
    OBU->>GW: [CFM] T-DISCONNECT.request CID_RBC1 cause=NORMAL_RELEASE
    GW->>RF1: [TCP] FIN dst=IP_RBC1:19990 PLMN-A
    RF1-->>TSGW_A: [5G] TCP close over PLMN-A DRB
    TSGW_A-->>RBC1: [TCP] FIN-ACK session released
    RBC1-->>RBC2: [NRBC] Handover Complete<br/>NID_NRBCMESSAGE HO_Complete | T_NRBC 32b | NID_ENGINE 32b
    Note over GW,RF1: [5G] Decision TOBA-7540 bearer management<br/>Option 1 - Detach PLMN-A NAS PDU Session Release vers AMF_A<br/>Option 2 - Maintien RF1 actif pour redondance radio

    Note over OBU,RBC2: Phase 7 - Operation nominale sous RBC2 PLMN-B
    OBU->>GW: [ETCS] T-DATA.request SafeData SUBSET-026 vers RBC2
    GW->>RF2: [TCP] dst=IP_RBC2:19990 PLMN-B
    RF2-->>TSGW_B: [5G] NR DRB PLMN-B session active
    TSGW_B-->>RBC2: [ETCS] EuroRadio session operationnelle PLMN-B
