Referentiel des payloads cles
Packet 131 - RBC Transition Order SUBSET-026-7 BL4 v4.0.0
Champ	Taille	Description
NID_PACKET	8 bits	= 131
Q_DIR	2 bits	0=reverse / 1=nominal / 2=both
L_PACKET	13 bits	Longueur totale typiquement 69 bits
Q_SCALE	2 bits	0=10cm / 1=1m / 2=10m
D_RBCTR	15 bits	Distance a la transition RBC
NID_C	10 bits	Country/region identity RBC acceptant
NID_RBC	14 bits	Identity RBC acceptant
NID_MN	24 bits 6x4b	PLMN ID MCC+MNC - PLMN-B si inter-reseau
Q_RBC	1 bit	0=last known RBC / 1=use phone number
PHONE_NUMBER	32 bits 8x4b	SIP URI ou adresse IP RBC acceptant
En FRMCS : NID_MN encode le PLMN ID. Si PLMN-B != PLMN-A, l OBU/GW detecte un changement de reseau et active la bearer flexibility scenario 2.
Messages SUBSET-026 - Session management
Msg	Nom	Emetteur	Champs cles
155	Initiation comm session	OBU->RBC	NID_MESSAGE 8b / T_TRAIN 32b / NID_ENGINE 32b
156	Termination comm session	OBU->RBC	NID_MESSAGE 8b / T_TRAIN 32b
32	RBC/RIU System Version	RBC->OBU	NID_MESSAGE 8b / T_TRAIN 32b / M_VERSION 7b
38	Initiation comm session	RBC->OBU	NID_MESSAGE 8b / T_TRAIN 32b / NID_LRBG 24b
39	Acknowledgement termination	RBC->OBU	NID_MESSAGE 8b / T_TRAIN 32b
24	General Message	RBC->OBU	NID_MESSAGE 8b / T_TRAIN 32b + packets optionnels
Primitives CFM - SUBSET-037-3 v4.1.4
Primitive	Direction	Parametres principaux
T-CONNECT.request	CFM User -> CFM	FRMCS_CED =
T-CONNECT.confirm	CFM -> CFM User	CID, status = OK/NOK
T-CONNECT.indication	CFM -> CFM User	CID, FRMCS_CED entrant
T-DATA.request	CFM User -> CFM	CID, SafeData SUBSET-037-2
T-DATA.indication	CFM -> CFM User	CID, SafeData recu
T-DISCONNECT.request	CFM User -> CFM	CID, cause NORMAL_RELEASE/ERROR
T-DISCONNECT.indication	CFM -> CFM User	CID, reason
SUBSET-037-3 par6.2.1.1.9 : "The interface is not mandatory. The service primitives describe the interface at a functional level."
Messages NRBC - SUBSET-039 v3.2.0
Message	Emetteur	Header 9 champs	Body
Handover Announcement	RBC1->RBC2	NID_NRBCMESSAGE / L_MESSAGE / T_NRBC 32b / NID_SENDER 14b / NID_RECEIVER 14b / NID_C_SENDER 10b / NID_C_RECEIVER 10b / NID_OPERATIONAL 32b / NID_ENGINE 32b	Train position, MA context
Handover Announcement ACK	RBC2->RBC1	idem	-
Train Accepted	RBC2->RBC1	idem	comm OBU etablie
Handover Complete	RBC1->RBC2	idem	-
