Comparaison synthetique
Dimension	Scenario 1 intra-PLMN	Scenario 2 inter-PLMN
Bearer 5G	PDU Session unique PLMN-A	2 PDU Sessions PLMN-A + PLMN-B
Modules RF	RF unique reutilise	RF1 PLMN-A + RF2 PLMN-B dual-attach
P131 NID_MN	NID_MN = PLMN-A	NID_MN = PLMN-B -> bearer flexibility
T-CONNECT CED	PLMN_A	PLMN_B -> GW route vers RF2
Coexistence sessions	Breve TCP setup ms	Prolongee Registration 5G + PDU Session s
Ref. SUBSET-026	par5.15 + P131	par5.15 + P131 NID_MN PLMN-B
Ref. SUBSET-037-3	T-CONNECT CED PLMN-A	T-CONNECT CED PLMN-B
Ref. TOBA	TOBA-7510 CFM	TOBA-7510 + TOBA-7540 bearer flexibility
Ref. 3GPP	Ng intra-AMF	Ng inter-AMF inter-PLMN Rel-15+
